data.description: Immaculate 2 Story Home that screams Pride of Ownership!  Walk to Parks and Schools! This 2014 home, with no Metro Tax, has been pre-inspected for your peace of mind.  It's almost impossible to find a home in more pristine condition. Modern grey hardwood floors gleam in natural light. Storybook Open Concept Layout with a modern kitchen. You'll fall in the love with the kitchen's sleek grey tiled backsplash, Stainless Steel Appliances, White Cabinets, and Granite of Course. Main level Bedroom could double as an office to "age in place". Enormous Upper Level Bedroom with private on-suite Master Bath. This spa-like  Master Bath offers a tiled walk in shower, a large walk-in closet, and more granite. Upper level boast a same level tiled laundry room for added convenience. Easy to maintain backyard and 600+ Square Foot Oversized Garage. Priced to sell, and the best value in Longmont. Showings begin at open house 11:00-1:00 P.M. on Saturday 9/25/2021.
